1
00:00:06,006 --> 00:00:09,384
SIRI ASLI KISSKH

2
00:00:18,977 --> 00:00:20,145
<i>Ik-jun?</i>

3
00:00:20,228 --> 00:00:21,730
Dia sanggup pergi ke Inje?

4
00:00:21,813 --> 00:00:23,481
<i>Ya, dia baru saja balik.</i>

5
00:00:24,149 --> 00:00:26,359
<i>- Dia siap beri saya duit.</i>
- Kenapa dengan dia?

6
00:00:26,443 --> 00:00:27,569
Tak pernah dia begitu.

7
00:00:27,652 --> 00:00:29,654
<i>Saya hampir menangis.</i>

8
00:00:29,738 --> 00:00:32,991
<i>Kami tak pernah ucap terima kasih
atau maaf</i>

9
00:00:33,074 --> 00:00:34,492
<i>kepada satu sama lain.</i>

10
00:00:34,576 --> 00:00:37,245
Tentulah saya tahu.
Keluarga saya pun sama.

11
00:00:38,288 --> 00:00:40,957
Aduhai. Saya rasa dia juga semakin tua.

12
00:00:41,541 --> 00:00:44,252
<i>- Awak dah balik?</i>
- Ya, tadi.

13
00:00:44,335 --> 00:00:47,505
Saya akan telefon apabila sampai
di kawasan rehat. Jumpa lagi.

14
00:01:00,977 --> 00:01:02,896
Semua nampak sedap. Nak pesan apa?

15
00:01:05,023 --> 00:01:07,358
- Apa yang awak buat?
- Ada rambut pada jaket awak.

16
00:01:13,031 --> 00:01:15,241
Awak perlu sentiasa makan ubat?

17
00:01:15,366 --> 00:01:18,620
Ya, ubat tahan sakit. Satu biji sehari.

18
00:01:19,871 --> 00:01:20,997
Awak kuat.

19
00:01:21,498 --> 00:01:23,500
Dah bertahun-tahun awak bertahan?

20
00:01:23,583 --> 00:01:24,918
Tapi saya dah okey sekarang.

21
00:01:25,502 --> 00:01:27,879
Macam Ik-sun, saya tak boleh
buat senaman berat,

22
00:01:27,962 --> 00:01:29,464
kecuali aktiviti harian.

23
00:01:29,547 --> 00:01:32,675
Ubat itu untuk sakit kronik saya.

24
00:01:32,759 --> 00:01:34,385
Tapi taklah sakit.

25
00:01:35,428 --> 00:01:36,638
Sabarlah setahun saja.

26
00:01:37,138 --> 00:01:38,932
Awak dah penat cari pengalaman.

27
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:41,810
Awak mesti tamatkan dengan baik
dan lulus peperiksaan.

28
00:01:43,144 --> 00:01:44,144
Ya.

29
00:01:44,813 --> 00:01:46,397
Saya ada di sisi awak, profesor.

30
00:01:49,108 --> 00:01:50,193
Apa cadangan awak?

31
00:01:50,777 --> 00:01:52,987
Pasta berkrim batang pinang kami
sangat digemari.

32
00:01:53,196 --> 00:01:55,573
Yang suka pasta minyak
pesan pasta telur ikan.

33
00:01:55,657 --> 00:01:56,741
Cepatnya dia sampai?

34
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,160
Di sini.

35
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:07,335
Profesor, awak dah tak makan laju.

36
00:02:07,752 --> 00:02:09,712
Kalau dulu, sekarang dah pencuci mulut.

37
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:11,881
Tak, ini lagi laju.

38
00:02:12,882 --> 00:02:14,300
Saya dah cuba perlahan.

39
00:02:14,884 --> 00:02:17,428
Makanan di sini sedap.
Seronok sekali-sekala makan luar.

40
00:02:19,222 --> 00:02:22,016
Seok-min, awak patut ulang kaji, bukan?
Peperiksaan dah dekat.

41
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:23,685
Ya, saya akan mula minggu depan.

42
00:02:24,853 --> 00:02:27,230
Macam mana kalau saya tak ada?
Awak akan bosan.

43
00:02:27,397 --> 00:02:29,774
- Saya akan melawat.
- Bilik belajar itu di mana?

44
00:02:29,858 --> 00:02:32,277
- Boleh kami jenguk?
- Hei, namanya bilik belajar.

45
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,279
Buat apa jenguk orang yang perlu belajar?

46
00:02:34,362 --> 00:02:36,489
Saya yang akan melawat. Aduhai.

47
00:02:37,490 --> 00:02:40,285
Seon-bin sayang, nanti tak ada orang
nak kacau awak lagi.

48
00:02:40,368 --> 00:02:41,744
Nanti awak bosan pula.

49
00:02:42,245 --> 00:02:43,245
"Seon-bin sayang"?

50
00:02:43,955 --> 00:02:45,707
Awak panggil "Seon-bin sayang"?

51
00:02:47,083 --> 00:02:48,334
Ahn Chi-hong sayang.

52
00:02:48,459 --> 00:02:50,503
Heo Seon-bin sayang
dan Profesor Chae sayang.

53
00:02:50,587 --> 00:02:53,673
Apa lagi... Ya, pasta sayang.

54
00:02:54,465 --> 00:02:57,802
Awak nampak mencurigakan.
Betulkah tak ada apa-apa?

55
00:02:57,886 --> 00:02:59,721
Apa yang awak cakap ini? Tak ada apa-apa.

56
00:02:59,804 --> 00:03:01,347
Profesor, nak pesan pencuci mulut?

57
00:03:01,431 --> 00:03:03,766
Aduhai, tengoklah dia cuba ubah topik.

58
00:03:04,392 --> 00:03:07,228
Betul, tak ada apa-apa.
Awak ingat saya ini apa?

59
00:03:08,104 --> 00:03:10,023
Hei, apa kurangnya saya?

60
00:03:10,106 --> 00:03:12,358
Dr. Yong sayang, awak sangat menarik.

61
00:03:12,442 --> 00:03:13,985
Saya tak layak cintakan awak.

62
00:03:14,068 --> 00:03:15,153
Dr. Yong sayang.

63
00:03:15,945 --> 00:03:18,865
Kata orang, bersin dan cinta
tak boleh disorok.

64
00:03:18,948 --> 00:03:20,033
Memang tak boleh sorok.

65
00:03:20,116 --> 00:03:21,492
Mesti ada apa-apa.

66
00:03:23,828 --> 00:03:25,413
Apa salahnya bercinta?

67
00:03:26,664 --> 00:03:28,917
Kami tak boleh bercinta
dengan rakan sekerjakah?

68
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:31,419
Kenapa tidak? Saya okey.

69
00:03:32,462 --> 00:03:34,255
Baguslah kalau boleh saling bergantung.

70
00:03:34,339 --> 00:03:35,339
Ya, betul.

71
00:03:37,008 --> 00:03:38,843
Saya dan Seon-bin sedang bercinta.

72
00:03:39,218 --> 00:03:41,596
Hei, Seon-bin. Kita bercinta, bukan?

73
00:03:42,722 --> 00:03:43,722
Mereka dah tahu.

74
00:03:44,349 --> 00:03:46,142
Macamlah ada orang nak percaya.

75
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:48,686
Siapa yang akan percaya?

76
00:03:51,606 --> 00:03:54,901
Dr. Yong, apa kita patut buat
dalam situasi ini?

77
00:03:54,984 --> 00:03:57,654
Apa pendapat awak?
Marilah kita pesan pencuci mulut.

78
00:03:58,780 --> 00:03:59,780
Maafkan saya!

79
00:04:09,582 --> 00:04:12,460
Apa nama kelab sosial ini?
"Saya <i>Gosu</i>" macam cikgu?

80
00:04:12,961 --> 00:04:14,921
<i>Ya. Saya</i> Gosu.

81
00:04:15,296 --> 00:04:17,131
<i>Saya jumpa mereka sebulan sekali,</i>

82
00:04:17,215 --> 00:04:19,384
<i>tapi saya tak boleh tahan lagi.</i>

83
00:04:19,759 --> 00:04:22,470
<i>Mereka paksa saya bawa awak.
Mereka betul-betul nak jumpa.</i>

84
00:04:23,263 --> 00:04:25,598
<i>Kita singgah dan makan malam
dengan mereka, okey?</i>

85
00:04:26,182 --> 00:04:27,517
Jangan buat saya begini.

86
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:30,603
Nampaknya awak betul-betul
nak tengok saya musnah.

87
00:04:30,687 --> 00:04:35,149
<i>Tak, mereka semua baik.
Mereka sangat naif dan jujur.</i>

88
00:04:35,233 --> 00:04:38,069
Tapi mesti mereka
dah tahap keempat atau kelima.

89
00:04:38,528 --> 00:04:40,905
Ik-sun, tekwando pun
saya tali pinggang jingga saja.

90
00:04:40,989 --> 00:04:42,573
Saya sama macam U-ju.

91
00:04:45,868 --> 00:04:47,620
Okey, kita pergi sama-sama.

92
00:04:47,704 --> 00:04:49,414
Saya kena ikut kalau kekasih ajak.

93
00:04:56,421 --> 00:04:57,421
Apa ini?

94
00:04:58,548 --> 00:05:00,008
Ini pun awak tak makan?

95
00:05:15,023 --> 00:05:16,316
- Helo.
- Helo.

96
00:05:16,668 --> 00:05:17,668
Helo.

97
00:05:17,692 --> 00:05:20,486
Helo, Prof. Kim. Gembira bertemu awak.

98
00:05:20,570 --> 00:05:22,739
Saya juga.
Terima kasih kerana menjemput saya.

99
00:05:22,822 --> 00:05:24,532
Ini Kapten Hong, yang nakal itu.

100
00:05:26,159 --> 00:05:28,661
Selepas hari itu, saya dah berubah.

101
00:05:29,037 --> 00:05:31,873
Malam itu,
Mejar Lee tak henti-henti sepak saya...

102
00:05:31,956 --> 00:05:33,041
- Oh...
- Hei!

103
00:05:36,002 --> 00:05:38,421
Saya ada sesuatu untuk awak.

104
00:05:40,298 --> 00:05:42,383
Terimalah, sebagai tanda minta maaf.

105
00:05:43,968 --> 00:05:45,261
Apa ini?

106
00:05:46,095 --> 00:05:47,096
<i>Gosu.</i> Ketumbar.

107
00:06:00,276 --> 00:06:01,319
Aduhai.

108
00:06:02,528 --> 00:06:03,571
Tengoklah kamu ini.

109
00:06:04,864 --> 00:06:05,864
Nah.

110
00:06:06,991 --> 00:06:08,951
Minumlah. Pandai.

111
00:06:09,911 --> 00:06:12,789
Kamu kata nak <i>tonkatsu</i>.
Tapi ini yang kamu teringin nak makan?

112
00:06:14,874 --> 00:06:16,959
U-ju, boleh ayah rasa sandwic kamu itu?

113
00:06:17,627 --> 00:06:18,711
Makanlah ayah punya.

114
00:06:23,049 --> 00:06:25,718
- Kamu nak rasa ayah punya?
- Saya dah makan semalam.

115
00:06:26,803 --> 00:06:29,222
Kamu ke sini semalam? Dengan siapa?

116
00:06:29,305 --> 00:06:30,890
Ayah tak tahu pun.

117
00:06:32,809 --> 00:06:33,976
Saya pelanggan tetap.

118
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,560
"Pelanggan tetap"?

119
00:06:36,229 --> 00:06:38,981
Wah. Kosa kata kamu dah berkembang.

120
00:06:39,107 --> 00:06:42,193
- Kamu datang dengan siapa?
- Mo-ne dan mak mentua saya.

121
00:06:44,904 --> 00:06:46,197
Mak mentua kamu?

122
00:06:46,781 --> 00:06:48,866
- U-ju, kamu tahu makna "mak mentua"?
- Ya.

123
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:50,535
Ibu kepada isteri.

124
00:06:56,374 --> 00:06:59,001
Saya lahirkan seorang genius ke dunia ini.

125
00:07:00,002 --> 00:07:01,212
Ayah.

126
00:07:03,089 --> 00:07:06,342
Saya nak satu lagi sandwic.

127
00:07:06,425 --> 00:07:09,137
Tapi sandwic itu ada separuh lagi.

128
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:11,264
Belikan satu lagi untuk saya.

129
00:07:12,807 --> 00:07:13,807
Buat muka comel.

130
00:07:17,728 --> 00:07:18,938
Jantung ayah...

131
00:07:32,201 --> 00:07:34,287
PROF. CHAE SONG-HWA

132
00:07:35,580 --> 00:07:37,206
Pesan dua. Apa-apa yang awak nak.

133
00:07:38,207 --> 00:07:39,917
Baik, saya nak <i>tonkatsu, udon,</i>

134
00:07:40,501 --> 00:07:42,420
nasi dengan telur ikan dan mi <i>soba </i>sejuk?

135
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:47,341
Mungkin yang lain akan makan sekali.

136
00:07:47,425 --> 00:07:49,302
Saya tak cakap apa-apa. Pesan sajalah.

137
00:07:49,385 --> 00:07:51,846
- Kenapa awak tercegat lagi? Masuklah.
- Sekejap.

138
00:07:53,473 --> 00:07:56,100
Awak tidurkah?
Awak macam dah hilang suara.

139
00:07:57,185 --> 00:07:58,311
Awak demam?

140
00:08:01,063 --> 00:08:02,231
Hidung tersumbat?

141
00:08:02,982 --> 00:08:05,568
Berhati-hati, terutamanya ketika
musim seperti sekarang.

142
00:08:06,027 --> 00:08:07,027
Awak dah makan?

143
00:08:10,406 --> 00:08:12,450
Okey, saya akan jaga makan.

144
00:08:13,659 --> 00:08:14,659
Selamat tinggal.

145
00:08:15,453 --> 00:08:16,496
Ya, saya cintakan awak.

146
00:08:17,121 --> 00:08:18,121
Jun-wan!

147
00:08:20,875 --> 00:08:22,919
- Awak tak reti ketukkah?
- Saya dah ketuk!

148
00:08:23,002 --> 00:08:25,296
Yakah? Apa? Apa yang awak nak?

149
00:08:25,379 --> 00:08:26,631
Saya tak ketuklah, gila.

150
00:08:26,714 --> 00:08:28,424
Buat apa ketuk masuk pejabat awak?

151
00:08:28,758 --> 00:08:31,719
Ada nombor Program Talian Hayat
dari Pusat Perubatan Kangwoon?

152
00:08:31,802 --> 00:08:34,096
Dia bantu hospital lain jugakah?

153
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:36,599
Ya, saya minta tolong dia baru-baru ini.

154
00:08:36,974 --> 00:08:39,852
Dia ada aliran wang tunai lebih agaknya.
Dia terus hantar duit.

155
00:08:40,353 --> 00:08:41,479
Dah hantar nombor dia.

156
00:08:41,604 --> 00:08:44,204
Hyeon Jeong-mi dari Jabatan Kebajikan
di Pusat Perubatan Kangwoon.

157
00:08:44,228 --> 00:08:47,109
Dia saja yang boleh tolong awak
hubungi Program Talian Hayat.

158
00:08:47,193 --> 00:08:49,153
- Ada kecemasankah?
- Tak.

159
00:08:49,237 --> 00:08:50,613
Untuk pesakit jangka panjang.

160
00:08:51,447 --> 00:08:53,241
Dia masih di sini sebab tak bayar bil.

161
00:08:53,324 --> 00:08:55,368
Saya rasa dia ambil
pinjaman berfaedah tinggi.

162
00:08:55,451 --> 00:08:57,328
Dah tua, tak ada keluarga atau kawan.

163
00:08:57,995 --> 00:09:00,122
Tapi dia ada rumah bujang
dan tinggal di situ,

164
00:09:00,206 --> 00:09:02,833
jadi dia tak penuhi
kriteria Jabatan Kebajikan. Rumitlah.

165
00:09:02,917 --> 00:09:05,211
Saya nak telefon dan tanya
boleh usahakan atau tak.

166
00:09:05,294 --> 00:09:07,338
- Awak dah makan?
- Saya ada pembedahan.

167
00:09:07,922 --> 00:09:09,257
Relakslah.

168
00:09:10,216 --> 00:09:13,344
Ya, betul. Pesakit adalah
lelaki berusia 78 tahun.

169
00:09:13,427 --> 00:09:16,180
Dia menjalani hemihepatektomi kanan

170
00:09:16,264 --> 00:09:17,848
disebabkan HCC.

171
00:09:18,266 --> 00:09:20,643
Dah lama dia ada di sini
sebab hati dia belum sembuh.

172
00:09:20,726 --> 00:09:24,564
<i>Okey. Saya akan ringkaskan
dan hantar ke Program Talian Hayat.</i>

173
00:09:25,022 --> 00:09:27,024
<i>Selalunya dia terus balas mesej saya.</i>

174
00:09:27,441 --> 00:09:29,860
<i>- Beri saya setengah jam.</i>
- Okey, terima kasih.

175
00:09:30,444 --> 00:09:34,115
Sekejap, dia doktorkah?

176
00:09:34,699 --> 00:09:36,576
Dia tanya soalan terperinci pesakit.

177
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:38,160
<i>Itu saya tak tahu.</i>

178
00:09:38,744 --> 00:09:40,997
<i>Saya rasa dia arif
dengan pengetahuan perubatan.</i>

179
00:09:41,163 --> 00:09:45,167
<i>Dia selalu tanya soalan terperinci
tentang keadaan pesakit.</i>

180
00:09:45,710 --> 00:09:47,253
<i>Saya akan hubungi awak semula.</i>

181
00:09:47,753 --> 00:09:48,753
Terima kasih.

182
00:09:49,130 --> 00:09:51,299
PROF. CHAE SONG-HWA

183
00:10:20,036 --> 00:10:21,621
DISEMBER 2019

184
00:10:22,288 --> 00:10:25,207
29 HARI BULAN
BERLEPAS

185
00:10:33,776 --> 00:10:34,776
Hai, mak.

186
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:37,303
Anak kesayangan mak yang comel buat apa?

187
00:10:37,386 --> 00:10:39,597
<i>- Nak pergi makan dengan Song-hwa.</i>
- Song-hwa?

188
00:10:40,556 --> 00:10:42,933
Bagus. Eloklah. Nak mak ikut sekali?

189
00:10:44,101 --> 00:10:45,895
Kami pesan makanan dari luar saja.

190
00:10:46,479 --> 00:10:49,523
Dan bukan Song-hwa. Mak salah faham.

191
00:10:49,607 --> 00:10:52,943
"Bukan Song-hwa"?
Maknanya kamu ada teman wanita.

192
00:10:53,027 --> 00:10:55,655
Siapa? Kahwin dengan dia. Kahwin sekarang.

193
00:10:55,738 --> 00:10:58,532
Pilihan mak Song-hwa,
tapi mak tak kisah siapa kamu pilih.

194
00:10:58,616 --> 00:11:00,576
Taklah. Saya tak bercinta dengan sesiapa.

195
00:11:00,660 --> 00:11:02,286
Saya tersilap cakap.

196
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:04,997
Mak, hujung minggu ini
saya ke Yangpyeong. Masakkan mi.

197
00:11:05,581 --> 00:11:08,000
Mak dan Jong-su nak pergi
lihat dedaun musim luruh.

198
00:11:08,292 --> 00:11:09,418
Datang minggu depan.

199
00:11:10,002 --> 00:11:13,005
Tapi kalau nak cakap hal itu,
mak tak nak jumpa. Jangan datang.

200
00:11:15,424 --> 00:11:16,801
Kita perlu berbincang.

201
00:11:17,593 --> 00:11:19,512
Pergilah makan tengah hari dengan En. Ju.

202
00:11:20,304 --> 00:11:21,305
Baiklah.

203
00:11:34,110 --> 00:11:36,070
- Dah panggil?
- Seok-hyeong ada pesakit.

204
00:11:36,153 --> 00:11:37,780
Jun-wan, bedah. Jeong-won, seminit.

205
00:11:37,863 --> 00:11:40,950
Hei, saya dengar Seok-hyeong
sangat popular di kalangan bakal ibu.

206
00:11:41,033 --> 00:11:43,202
Jangan merepek.

207
00:11:43,702 --> 00:11:45,496
Dia begitu hanya dengan kita.

208
00:11:45,579 --> 00:11:49,083
Kakak ipar kawan saya ialah pesakit dia,

209
00:11:49,166 --> 00:11:51,168
dia kata Seok-hyeong lelaki paling baik.

210
00:11:51,252 --> 00:11:53,170
Aduhai, susah saya nak percaya.

211
00:11:56,132 --> 00:11:58,259
Hei! Saya gelisah kalau awak buat begitu.

212
00:11:58,342 --> 00:12:00,177
Kenapa... Kalaulah boleh tumbuk awak.

213
00:12:00,261 --> 00:12:02,596
Guna saja yang ini.

214
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:05,099
Awak tak tentu arah.
Awak ikut perangai siapa?

215
00:12:07,309 --> 00:12:08,978
U-ju. Semuanya daripada dia.

216
00:12:10,438 --> 00:12:12,690
Baiklah. Aduh, sakitnya.

217
00:12:14,567 --> 00:12:15,776
Itu dia.

218
00:12:18,237 --> 00:12:20,823
- Tunggu.
- Apa? Ada apa?

219
00:12:21,407 --> 00:12:23,159
